","publishedAt":"2017-01-22T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"1.9 g","fat":"11 g","uom":"per 1 portions","carbohydrates":"18 g","calories":"753 kJ \/ 179 kcal"},"usefulItems":"baking tray (20 x 30 cm), baking paper, 8 ramekins or dariole moulds (150 ml), popsicle sticks , aluminium foil, oven, freezer","hintsAndTricks":["Macadamia crumble can be made in advance and stored in a sealable container in the refrigerator for up to 2 days.","You can substitute fresh mango with frozen mango.","If you do not have icy-pole moulds, set mixture in a terrine mould or slice tin lined with baking paper and slice to serve.","Cream can be omitted to make a dairy-free dessert.","Macadamias can be omitted to make a nut-free dessert."],"basicInfo":["easy","30m","7h 45m","8 portions"]}